<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>自从孩子们拯救了火车之后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>连着几个晚上，鲍比都做了噩梦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，他们收到了一封信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信是写给彼得、鲍比和菲利斯的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们好奇地打开信。信上写着：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亲爱的先生和小姐：谢谢你们拯救了火车，避免了一个重大的事故。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请于本月30号下午3点来火车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>英格伍德——南北铁路公司秘书</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是个令人十分难忘的一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下午3点，孩子们穿着他们最好的衣服，来到了火车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站长过来迎接他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请跟我来候车室吧。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天的候车室看上去很不一样：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地上铺着地毯，窗台上摆放着玫瑰花，墙上挂着绿色的树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站台工作人员帕克斯和其他几位戴着高帽子的男人站在一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边还有几位穿着华丽的女士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最棒的是，火车上的那位老先生也在那里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走过来跟孩子们握手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一位看上去很重要的人站了起来，他描述了孩子们勇敢的事迹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，老先生站起来，也说了一些夸奖孩子们的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，他一一叫了孩子们的名字，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>送给他们每人一只漂亮的金表和一条表链。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>表里写着一段话：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你非常勇敢！感谢你阻止了一起火车事故！——铁路公司董事会”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站长小声对鲍比说：“现在你得说点什么，感谢一下大家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他轻轻地把鲍比推上前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“女士们，先生们，”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感谢你们送了这么漂亮的怀表，我们有些惭愧，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我们其实并没有做什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗯……那确实是一件让人兴奋又害怕的事情……谢谢大家！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都热烈地鼓掌，然后每个人都和孩子们握了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>多么美好的一天啊！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后，老先生和他们一起来到他们的白房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想见见这么勇敢又聪明的孩子们的妈妈。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈看到客人，非常惊讶！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她再次感谢老先生在她生病时送来东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一边喝茶，一边听孩子们讲述在火车站里发生的事情，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈还和老先生用了法语和英语聊天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老先生要离开时，妈妈说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴见到您，感谢您所做的一切！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们向老先生挥手说再见，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像每天早上他的火车经过时那样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>